text: Rhytidothyra is a genus of land snails with an operculum, terrestrial gastropod mollusks in the family Pomatiidae."Mollusca" . Diversidad Biológica Cubana, accessed 23 March 2011. == Species == Species within the genus Rhytidothyra include: * Rhytidothyra bilabiata (d’Orbigny, 1842) * Rhytidothyra jacobsoni Alcalde, 1948 == References == Category:Pomatiidae
